Next, you could then make a task for each possible phrase the user could say. If the phrase is &quot;press 1&quot;, you could redirect to a [Twilio Function][6] that uses `sendDigits` to play DTMF tones when the call is answered. The Twilio Autopilot task could include this JSON:
```
{
